metadata.name: Anthozoa#1
metadata.description:
Working with top 3D designers in the world, DANZ is bringing the latest technology to create digital couture garments inspired by the Underwater World. Not only are the items gender neutral, they also exist beyond the limitations of size and fit, while blurring the boundaries of virtual and reality.
Together, let us escape Into the metaverse of the Great Abyss.

Welcome to the future.
